      "text": "Machine Boundary\nThe machine structure turns motor torque\ninto tool motion through real stiffness,\nbacklash, friction, and thermal growth.",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 17.5,
      "containerId": "node-11cc460fcb64",
      "originalText": "Machine Boundary\nThe machine structure turns motor torque into tool motion through real stiffness, backlash, friction, and thermal growth.",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "autoResize": true,
      "customData": {
        "node_id": "machine-boundary"
      }
    },
