      "text": "Controller Layer\nThe CNC controller is the\nmachine-level decision maker. It\ndecides what motion should happen,\nnot how motor current is switched.",
      "fontSize": 18,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 22.5,
      "containerId": "node-7ef950708a9b",
