      "text": "What A Drive Does\nA motor drive is a controlled power\namplifier between low-energy controller\ncommands and high-energy motor windings.",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 17.5,
      "containerId": "node-cd75dccb0df7",
