      "text": "Grounding And Bonding\nGrounding is for fault safety and reference\ncontrol. Shielding is for noise control.\nThey touch, but they are not the same idea.",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 17.5,
      "containerId": "node-4c13b0e33129",
      "originalText": "Grounding And Bonding\nGrounding is for fault safety and reference control. Shielding is for noise control. They touch, but they are not the same idea.",
